23:50.062 --> 23:52.486
It was like... A nice, solid Carnegie library.

23:52.506 --> 23:53.307
It was incredible.

23:54.028 --> 23:57.413
It had two sets of stacks.

23:59.080 --> 24:05.147
two sets of stacks that I believe would have worked out to about 25 linear miles of shelf space.

24:05.167 --> 24:06.808
