25:26.809 --> 25:28.492
And that was the point of the whole exercise.

25:28.813 --> 25:32.960
Okay, and then what is the... We called that the grand mea culpa, you know.

25:33.080 --> 25:34.984
The grand mea culpa.

25:35.004 --> 25:35.104
Okay.

25:35.124 --> 25:38.730
I cop.

25:40.364 --> 25:46.070
