well the affinity the affinity center steven culture created the affinity centers to get the money that they because they didn't have enough money and they wanted to and they and then also the affinity centers and those people are going to be real upset when eventually this the truth comes out if it ever does um were basically a smoke screen for the corporations that were going in the corporations got

